OL,5, A US court has blocked a $2.2bn        
OL,6, (#1.9bn) merger between the world's    
OL,7, largest book publisher Penguin Random  
OL,8, House and its rival Simon & Schuster.  
OL,10,FIn a brief order on Monday, US District
OL,11,FJudge Florence Pan said the deal could 
OL,12,F"substantially" lessen competition in  
OL,13,Fthe publishing industry.               
OL,15,FThe US Department of Justice filed a   
OL,16,Flawsuit to stop the deal last November.
OL,18,FPenguin Random House was formed through
OL,19,Fthe merger of two major publishers from
OL,20,Fthe UK and the US in 2013.             
